Career/Employability/Learning Insights
With the CMS systems constantly evolving and developing employers expect the employes to be able to chase and learn new advances in the systems as well as 
be intrested in learning the development and feature of the upcomming ubdates and patches. Along with this the understanding of CMS systems are able to colaborate and work on diffrent aspects of buiness potentual 
from marketing to custumer support and asthetics of development of UX/UI.Knowing how to work with popular CMS tools like WordPress, Drupal, or Joomla can make you more attractive to potential employers, especially in roles related to web development, content creation, and digital marketing.
